definitions.definition: A state of unconsciousness from which one may not wake up, usually induced by some form of trauma .

main_definition: A state of unconsciousness from which one may not wake up, usually induced by some form of trauma .

definitions.definition: A cloud of dust surrounding the nucleus of a comet .
A defect characterized by diffuse , pear - shaped images that in an ideal image would appear as points .
A tuft or bunch , such as the assemblage of branches forming the head of a tree, a cluster of bracts when empty and terminating the inflorescence of a plant, or a tuft of long hairs on certain seeds.

main_definition: ( astronomy ) A cloud of dust surrounding the nucleus of a comet .
secondary_definitions: ( optics ) A defect characterized by diffuse , pear - shaped images that in an ideal image would appear as points .

( botany ) A tuft or bunch , such as the assemblage of branches forming the head of a tree, a cluster of bracts when empty and terminating the inflorescence of a plant, or a tuft of long hairs on certain seeds.
